(122, 1, '2013-11-27 13:51:12', '2013-11-27 13:51:12', '<!--:en--><h1>Why <span style="color: #339966;">Spiralps?</span></h1>\n<strong>Spiralps® is a new type of natural drink, the first of its kind containing fresh microalgae Spirulina. </strong>\n\nThe fresh Spirulina in Spiralps® not only tastes great, (far better than any dried form) it is nutritionally superior, too!\n\nOur Spirulina is <strong> not cultivated out in an open pond, but in a controlled environment, to guarantee the highest quality.</strong> Furthermore, our Spirulina has <strong>never been heated</strong>, thanks to an advanced high-pressure pasteurization system that preserves nutritional values.\n\nSpiralps® is produced in <strong>Switzerland</strong> and contains herb-extracts from the pristine Alps and organic-fruits, combining the benefits of all these raw ingredients, to deliver more, natural vitamins, carotenoids, antioxidants, and fibers.\n\n<strong>Spiralps® is THE solution for consumers that are looking for a "wellness" drink that helps them boost their vital-energy level, fight fatigue, combat stress, and live healthy.</strong>\n\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-121" alt="banner_product_page" src="http://spiralps.ch/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/banner_product_page.jpg" width="878" height="430" />\n<ul class="props1">\n	<li>100% Natural with Fresh Spirulina &amp; Organic Fruits</li>\n	<li>NO chemicals, NO e-series, NO preservatives, NO additives</li>\n	<li>Never heated to preserve its intrinsic superior qualities</li>\n	<li>Not just another watered down mix with the minimal percentages</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Ingredients:</h2>\nCrystal clear Alpine mountain water, organic apples, organic peaches, apple sweetener, fresh Spirulina, organic lemon, Alpine herbal extracts, natural flavor.\n\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-123" alt="nur_fact" src="http://spiralps.ch/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/nur_fact.png" width="327" height="72" />\n\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-125" alt="big_shadow" src="http://spiralps.ch/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/big_shadow.png" width="922" height="43" />\n<h1>Benefits of <span style="color: #339966;">Spiralps</span></h1>\n<h2><img class="size-full wp-image-127 alignleft" alt="round_image_01" src="http://spiralps.ch/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/round_image_01.png" width="111" height="112" />The First Fresh Spirulina Drink Worldwide</h2>\nTo guarantee top quality, Spiralps® contains Spirulina produced in a controlled environment and added fresh â not dried. Spiralps® is pasteurized with a new cold (high-pressure) technique, which does not need to heat the product to preserve its best qualities.\n<h2></h2>\n<h2><img class="size-full wp-image-129 alignleft" alt="round_image_02" src="http://spiralps.ch/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/round_image_02.png" width="111" height="112" />Complete And Healthy Drink</h2>\nBy combining the benefits of our fresh Spirulina, with the benefits of the herbal extracts and organic fruits Spiralps® is naturally more complete, containing more vitamins, antioxidants, and fiber than any comparable drink made from dried Spirulina\n<h2></h2>\n<h2><img class="size-full wp-image-131 alignleft" alt="round_image_03" src="http://spiralps.ch/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/round_image_03.png" width="111" height="112" />Natural Wellness Drink</h2>\nSpiralps® contains no additives, only natural ingredients. We have added Alpine herbs to the mix, not only for the taste, but also more importantly for their recognized properties. For example, thyme contributes to the stimulation of immunity, juniper aiding digestion. We still have other herbs in our drink, but these are kept secret ...\n<h2></h2>\n<h2><img class="size-full wp-image-133 alignleft" alt="round_image_04" src="http://spiralps.ch/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/round_image_04.png" width="111" height="112" />Tasty &amp; Low In Calories</h2>\nCompared to dried Spirulina, fresh Spirulina tastes good. Combined with the herbal extracts and organic fruit puree, Spiralps® is refreshing and has the taste of juicy fresh peaches. Spiralps® is sweetened naturally with fruits and is low in calories. Spiralps®, as a fresh product, is extremely perishable and must be stored in the refrigerator not more than two months.\n<h2><img class="size-full wp-image-134 alignleft" alt="round_image_05" src="http://spiralps.ch/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/round_image_05.png" width="111" height="112" />"Swiss Made"</h2>\nSpiralps® is produced in the Swiss Alps; at the foot of the mountains near the Rhône River in an area called Valais (see www.valais.ch). All the steps in producing Spiralps® are carefully monitored, creating a top quality product with a high level of traceability. Special efforts are invested into quality control, especially in the strict monitoring of the heavy metal content, and microbiology.\n<h2></h2>\n<h2><img class="size-full wp-image-135 alignleft" alt="round_image_06" src="http://spiralps.ch/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/round_image_06.png" width="111" height="112" />Organic</h2>\nSpiralps® is an organic product certified by Bio Inspecta AG. Our apples are grown near our production site; the peaches and lemons come from sunny Spain. With the climate changes, maybe "soon" we will be ready to grow lemons in Switzerland ;-).<!--:--><!--:de-->Why Spiralps?\n\n<strong>Spiralps® is a new type of natural drink, the first of its kind containing fresh microalgae Spirulina. </strong>\n\nThe fresh Spirulina in Spiralps® not only tastes great, (far better than any dried form) it is nutritionally superior, too!\n\nOur Spirulina is <strong> not cultivated out in an open pond, but in a controlled environment, to guarantee the highest quality.</strong> Furthermore, our Spirulina has <strong>never been heated</strong>, thanks to an advanced high-pressure pasteurization system that preserves nutritional values.\n\nSpiralps® is produced in <strong>Switzerland</strong> and contains herb-extracts from the pristine Alps and organic-fruits, combining the benefits of all these raw ingredients, to deliver more, natural vitamins, carotenoids, antioxidants, and fibers.\n\n<strong>Spiralps® is THE solution for consumers that are looking for a "wellness" drink that helps them boost their vital-energy level, fight fatigue, combat stress, and live healthy.</strong><!--:--><!--:fr-->Why Spiralps?\n\n<strong>Spiralps® is a new type of natural drink, the first of its kind containing fresh microalgae Spirulina. </strong>\n\nThe fresh Spirulina in Spiralps® not only tastes great, (far better than any dried form) it is nutritionally superior, too!\n\nOur Spirulina is <strong> not cultivated out in an open pond, but in a controlled environment, to guarantee the highest quality.</strong> Furthermore, our Spirulina has <strong>never been heated</strong>, thanks to an advanced high-pressure pasteurization system that preserves nutritional values.\n\nSpiralps® is produced in <strong>Switzerland</strong> and contains herb-extracts from the pristine Alps and organic-fruits, combining the benefits of all these raw ingredients, to deliver more, natural vitamins, carotenoids, antioxidants, and fibers.\n\n<strong>Spiralps® is THE solution for consumers that are looking for a "wellness" drink that helps them boost their vital-energy level, fight fatigue, combat stress, and live healthy.</strong><!--:-->', '<!--:en-->Spiralps Natural Drink<!--:--><!--:de-->Spiralps Natural Drink<!--:--><!--:fr-->Spiralps Natural Drink<!--:-->', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '68-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-11-27 13:51:12', '2013-11-27 13:51:12', '', 68, 'http://spiralps.ch/uncategorized/68-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
